txt.en: Vale-flies and biting vale-gnats can be found in the Beorning-lands.\n\nYou should defeat vale-flies and biting vale-gnats.
You have defeated many vale-flies and biting vale-gnats, which will surely bring some relief to the farmers in the Beorning-lands.
Swarming gnats and pesky flies in the Beorning-lands are hard to bear, even for a Beorning. You should defeat these annoying insects. Those in the Beorning-lands will be pleased with your efforts.
